<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .application-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🏠 Application Received</h1>
        <p>Your tenant screening application has been successfully submitted</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{applicantName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for submitting your tenant screening application! We have successfully received your application and it is now being processed.</p>

        <div class="application-details">
            <h3>📋 Application Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Application Number:</strong> {{applicationNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Property:</strong> {{propertyName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Submission Date:</strong> {{submissionDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> Submitted - Under Review</p>
        </div>

        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>🚀 Next Steps</h3>
            <p>{{nextSteps}}</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Background check will be initiated within 24 hours</li>
                <li>Credit report will be requested with your consent</li>
                <li>We may contact you for additional documentation</li>
                <li>Rental history verification will be conducted</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight">
            <h3>📧 What to Expect</h3>
            <p>You will receive email notifications at each stage of the screening process. The typical timeline is:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Day 1-2:</strong> Initial review and document verification</li>
                <li><strong>Day 2-3:</strong> Background and credit checks</li>
                <li><strong>Day 3-5:</strong> Final review and decision</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{applicationUrl}}" class="button">View Application Status</a>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Important:</strong> Please keep this email for your records. Your application number is {{applicationNumber}}.</p>

        <p>If you have any questions about your application or the screening process, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        Property Management Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Property Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
